<div id="post-737" class="cf post-737 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-uncategorized">

	<h2>
		<span class="post-format"></span>
		<a href="http://werblog.com/2003/04/the-internet-story-all-over-again/" title="The Internet story all over again" rel="bookmark">The Internet story all over again</a>
		
